title: Windows10_InsiderPreview_x64_EN-US_10162 ]junoliv69]
description:
Microsoft has released the 32-bit (x86) and 64-bit (x64) ISO images for Windows 10 Build 10162, the most updated official preview build of Windows 10 available. Contrary to Microsoft tradition to release a build to Slow ring and ISOs at the same time, the ISO images for build 10162 are published to Windows Insider website ahead of the flight of the build on the Slow ring.

Gabriel Aul, General Manager of OSG Data and Fundamentals team in Microsoft, tweeted the release of Windows 10 Build 10162 ISOs on Twitter:

Windows 10 Pro Insider Preview10.0.10162(esd)(x64)(2015)
 
Mode:Bootable
Upgrade:You can upgrade just run setup.exe from iso or extract the iso and run setup.exe and follow the steps...
Keys:Same keys with build 10158 works and no need tools for activation..when you put on of keys of preview build 10158 or 10159 they activated
